{"tid":2005229,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲警：無港警雙手離軚做法","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T13:02:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d55628c8610afbf7053d97825d6f72899b860cc","tid":2005229,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200507/U6V42IBECZMLGVBCMCOBLGJI2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2FU6V42IBECZMLGVBCMCOBLGJI2Q%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdRd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=6ca28917\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2FU6V42IBECZMLGVBCMCOBLGJI2Q%2F&h=d0ffd340\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200507/U6V42IBECZMLGVBCMCOBLGJI2Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲警：無港警雙手離軚做法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200507/large/1588784548_5015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200507%2Flarge%2F1588784548_5015.jpg&h=194d04fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方堅稱交通警雙手離軚行車的做法無錯。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港警察多次遭踢爆發表不實言論。警方早前辯稱有外國案例支持交通警雙手離軚的做法，其後說不出案例編號，改口指是與澳洲警方交流時學習此技。立法會議員朱凱廸向澳洲警方查詢事件，對方近日回覆稱他們並無這個「駕駛技術」，更沒有和港警的相關通訊紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n3月5日一名交通警護送車隊往駿洋邨時，曾雙手離開電單車軚盤，並以。。。。。。。。。。。係有咁嘅案例」，惟本報追問多日後，警方始終無法提供案例編號。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸其後多次去信政府要求交代外國案例詳情，上月警務。。。。。。。。。。。在交流活動中，向港警示範處理不同個案的駕駛技巧。<br />\n朱凱廸：睇鄧炳強點兜<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸繼續追問，警方回應指2013年香港警隊護送組成員赴澳洲與維多利亞。。。。。。。。。。。。不同個案的駕駛技巧。<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸表示就此去信澳洲維多利亞警隊，對方近日回覆稱並無使用相關。。。。。。。。。。。。題時只是信口開河，「總之差人做嘢就唔會錯。現在被澳洲警隊一下KO，且看鄧炳強仲點樣兜」。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆時堅稱，2013年三名警員曾赴澳洲與維多利亞警隊。。。。。。。。。。。關文章印證，但該篇文章並無具體介紹對方所作的示範。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳建平"},{"pid":"812741a830ef27e598aeba5521853b613108ea44","tid":2005229,"uid":60259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:38:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09248bd5aa73aba5999cc81b99696ef07ec600a8","tid":2005229,"uid":20867,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://michellecuizonfernandez.files.wordpress.com/2014/06/titanic-movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmichellecuizonfernandez.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F06%2Ftitanic-movie.jpg&h=92ff1e3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d8a2f32d06dd2ca726dbcd16e5d678a9e026cf3","tid":2005229,"uid":271199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dn166eB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDn166eB.gif&h=c79e93a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ab536e3795fdb3ee8a08603342fcef8ca01a710","tid":2005229,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35dfde2c9fe82900de7b6beb87966e22b127dd6","tid":2005229,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4e4d2ca21be4fa468836bb365abbd5ba03a499","tid":2005229,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3190efb741ff7c4f80c35ac13aee0c74554488","tid":2005229,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"為左洗甩真係亂噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe45b0a280f67d931c7f7f77936600715f5a9bf","tid":2005229,"uid":11919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"拉澳洲警返黎坐啦吊 犯